sequenceDiagram
  autonumber

  participant MA as AI Applications
  participant AT as AIOps Telemetry Platform

  box rgb(230, 255, 235) 
    participant INV as Log Analysis Agents Layer
  end

  participant RM as AIOPS Remediation Plane

  MA->>AT: Telemetry ingestion request (trace + spans)
  AT->>AT: Escalation loop + NFR detection\ncreates issue
  AT->>INV: Analysis handoff\n(trace_id, timestamp, agent_name)
  INV->>INV: 5-agent pipeline + persist trace_results
  INV-->>AT: RCA + recommendations payload
  AT->>AT: Store in issue_analyses + dashboard surfaces

  Note over AT,RM: Remediation flow is separate and typically UI-triggered
  AT->>RM: Remediation workflow handoff calls
  RM->>RM: Project resolution -> plan -> implementation -> review -> PR
  RM-->>AT: Status + artifact updates
